&lt;p&gt;아침에 운동 다녀올 때 보니 벚꽃이 활짝 펴 있었다. 보정하고 컴터로 옮길 걸 그랬나?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;엄청 이뻤는데 사진이 다 표현하지 못하는 것 같다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class="gallery-image" data-flex-basis="320px" data-flex-grow="133" height="3024" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px" src="https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040302/2.jpg" srcset="https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040302/2_hu_93d02f8e7aa2e9a.jpg 800w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040302/2_hu_2197811637ba5100.jpg 1600w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040302/2_hu_10225b455240ef03.jpg 2400w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040302/2.jpg 4032w" width="4032"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;올 해는 같이 벚꽃 볼 사람이 있었으면 좋겠다&amp;hellip;.했는데&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class="gallery-image" data-flex-basis="320px" data-flex-grow="133" height="3024" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px" src="https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040302/3.jpg" srcset="https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040302/3_hu_7214bdd57f7458ca.jpg 800w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040302/3_hu_c30cbed4b7cf717.jpg 1600w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040302/3_hu_f2c4a4ca18ac3ca1.jpg 2400w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040302/3.jpg 4032w" width="4032"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;결국 혼자 본다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;나는 남자친구로는 영 꽝인가보다..&lt;/p&gt;
